	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001187_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'--> 
<addSpan spanTo="#p1r-01" place="marginleft"><!--addSpan/@place='left margin of fol. 1r'--></addSpan>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">not too late for reversing my decision 
<lb/>about getting the medicines in <placeName>Edinburgh</placeName><reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I am &amp; 
<lb/><persName>David Livingstone</persName>
<lb/></p><anchor xml:id="p1r-01"/>
<!-- headed notepaper --><!--<p rend="right"><placeName>45 Whitehall Pl. </placeName> <lb/></p>-->
<lb/><p rend="right">22<hi rend="sup">d</hi> Jany 
<lb/><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>1858 </p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear Sir </p>
<lb/><p><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>On counselling 
<lb/><persName>Captain Washington</persName>
<lb/>about the paper 
<lb/>for drying plants 
<lb/>he informed me 
<lb/>that he has got 
<lb/>five reams of 
<lb/>it ready for you<reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001187_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>He thinks that 
<lb/>after you have 
<lb/>made the list 
<lb/>complete it ought 
<lb/>to be sent to 
<lb/>the medical depart
<lb/>ment of the 
<lb/>Navy and that 
<lb/>the medicines 
<lb/>should be furnished 
<lb/>by them. So if 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001187_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>you have not 
<lb/>already ordered 
<lb/>any you had 
<lb/>better just send 
<lb/>me the list 
<lb/>and if you 
<lb/>should come to 
<lb/><placeName>London</placeName> you 
<lb/>could see to 
<lb/>the packing of 
<lb/>them as you 
<lb/>desire<reg>.</reg></p>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001187_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'-->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">Please name arsenical soap corrosive 
<lb/>sublimate &amp;c in your list<reg>.</reg></p><lb/>
<lb/>
<p rend="no-indent">If convenient it 
<lb/>would be well 
<lb/>for you to see 
<lb/><persName>Captain Washington</persName>
<lb/>before we go. He 
<lb/>likes to be <hi rend="underline"><choice><sic><w>acknow-<lb break="no"/>ledged</w></sic><corr>acknowleged</corr></choice></hi> and is also 
<lb/>very useful in getting 
<lb/>anything for you 
<lb/>in his power. 
<lb/>A quarter or half 
<lb/>a year's salary may 
<lb/>be obtained. </p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">Hoping that this is </p> 

			
